    "body": "<span class=\"solution-visible-txt\">All submissions for this problem are available.</span><p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>Chef was home on a Sunday morning and was playing with ones and zeros. His best friend Chefu came to him to solve a problem where he wants to get the minimum number which can be formed by <b>N ones</b> and <b>M zeros</b> (in binary) provided that the most significant position should have a 1. Chef gave the solution, but Chefu forgot it so he wants you to help him get the answer (in decimal) once again.</p>\n\n\n<h3>Input</h3>\n<p>The first line of the input contains <b>T</b>, the number of test case.</p>\n<p>Each test case consists of one line containing the two integers <b>N</b>, the number of 1's, and <b>M</b>, the number of 0's.</p>\n<b>Note: Please trim trailing whitespaces</b>\n<p> </p>\n\n\n<h3>Output</h3>\n<p>For every test case, output one integer which is the answer to the question.</p>\n\n\n<h3>Constraints</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><b>1</b> \u2264 <b>T</b> \u2264 <b>10<sup>5</sup></b></li>\n<li><b>1</b> \u2264 <b>N</b> \u2264 <b>60</b></li>\n<li><b>0</b> \u2264 <b>M</b> \u2264 <b>59</b></li>\n<li><b>1</b> \u2264 <b>N+M</b> \u2264 <b>60</b></li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n\n\n<h3>Example</h3>\n<pre><b>Input:</b>\n4\n1 1\n3 2\n1 0\n4 4\n\n<b>Output:</b>\n2\n19\n1\n135\n</pre>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n\n<h3>Explanation</h3>\n<p><b>Test case 1:</b>The minimum number formed is 10 in binary which is 2 in decimal.</p>\n",
